== Info ==

Version 0.1.0: hopefully installable, runnable and usable

Various plugins bundled: 
  - Clock
  - CPULoad
  - Flexible space
  - MemInfo
  - Menu
  - MusicControl
  - Pager
  - QuickTerminal
  - Separator
  - VolumeControl

Themes included:
  - SolidBlue

== Help ==

To install Foopanel, just run from a root shell:
  python setup.py install
  
Then, to run it, simply type "foopanel" in a shell.
  